{"tid":1999994,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"黃金周搞手笑言成效獲黨認證","createTime":"2020-05-03T14:12:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-03T14:44:46.000Z","uid":25558,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"4d191c29f6f9c81a928cef797f21bfdb5e20d934","tid":1999994,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T14:12:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200503/JBV2YLA3JMVNPKUIZVL66K6HX4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200503%2FJBV2YLA3JMVNPKUIZVL66K6HX4%2F&d=5G%2Bx0n%2BFJXS0hP%2BJIuhjgvUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=8f9481a5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200503%2FJBV2YLA3JMVNPKUIZVL66K6HX4%2F&h=3d2eadb6\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200503/JBV2YLA3JMVNPKUIZVL66K6HX4/</a><br />\n<br />\n黃金周搞手笑言成效獲黨認證<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200503/large/1588435950_f163.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200503%2Flarge%2F1588435950_f163.gif&h=5e117ed6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】「黃金周支援黃店計劃」連續三日盛況空前，中聯辦昨日發聲明批評黃色經濟圈是「政治綁架經濟的政。。。。。<br />\n「香港良心Guide」創辦人Tommy（圖）笑言再次獲得「黨嘅認證」，認為全因活動具成效，讓黃店得益，才會吸引中聯辦及親共媒體抨擊。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：西環狙擊黃圈 斥「綁架經濟」 戴耀廷反駁：圖剝奪港人消費自由<br />\n<br />\n受惠黃店：五一生意如過年<br />\n<br />\nTommy接受本報訪問指，受疫情影響，黃店生意大受打擊，但黃金周開始三日以來，很多黃店大排長龍，估計合共有約數十萬人參與，創造逾億元生意額。他認為黃金。。。。。。<br />\n的消費習慣，又指數字反映「好多人都係未放棄呢場運動，都搵緊唔同方法抗爭，之前因為肺炎影響，大家好似淡咗，其實需要一啲渠道抒發想繼續抗爭嘅感受，黃金周就做到呢個效果」。<br />\n<br />\nTommy認為政治與經濟、生活是息息相關，「政治綁架經濟」之說並不成立。至於有親中媒體頭版質疑「食個飯都要睇顏色？」Tommy解釋香港是有自由的地方，市民。。。。。。。<br />\n權必然大力反對，「但奈何暫時未搵到方法對付我哋，咪用報紙、聲明去『大』我哋囉」。<br />\n<br />\n在「黃金周支援黃店計劃」下，多間黃店的生意錄得佳績，粉嶺華心街市營業的「華心鮮果」老闆娘黃小姐（圖）表示，。。。。。。<br />\n，我最開心唔係錢，係原來咁多人撐我」，即使面對逆境，她指從不後悔自己表態，患難中見到同路人支持十分感動，「我本身又姓黃，起碼對得住自己個姓。」<br />\n<br />\n■記者陳詠恩"},{"pid":"91fdac53519c83bebad0b7aa772ebdcecb8f175e","tid":1999994,"uid":133086,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T14:25:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5A0vjUJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5A0vjUJ.jpg&h=5e33363e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c74ab66df4368144b1060bda0fc39be82d09548b","tid":1999994,"uid":66798,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T14:37:03.000Z","msg":"白兵/熱狗/中聯辦都好驚黃色經濟圈<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0052b2a5071d2ffb7a45c6a6904723e12bb32245","tid":1999994,"uid":53612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T14:38:22.000Z","msg":"黃藍地圖<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/maps/NPYFzo1P4zpyQ8Vm9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fmaps%2FNPYFzo1P4zpyQ8Vm9&d=5G%2Bx0n%2BFJXS0hP%2BJIuhjgvUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=e55b4aed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/maps/NPYFzo1P4zpyQ8Vm9</a>"},{"pid":"2b249f257543f81d4636bb0c116ae9d64b6ab3e6","tid":1999994,"uid":48040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T14:40:40.000Z","msg":"多謝手足 辛苦手足<br />\n----------------<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9rjWZ26.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9rjWZ26.png&h=89b8261c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/dp/B087G3LZCH/ref=cm_sw_r_tw_dp_U_x_BBQOEbNQEPT2J\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB087G3LZCH%2Fref%3Dcm_sw_r_tw_dp_U_x_BBQOEbNQEPT2J&d=5G%2Bx0n%2BFJXS0hP%2BJIuhjgvUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=5731a463\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.amazon.com/dp/B087G3LZCH/ref=cm_sw_r_tw_dp_U_x_BBQOEbNQEPT2J</a>"},{"pid":"9bff3732567cab6a655d88fbe5cdf4c388da6dfb","tid":1999994,"uid":254450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T14:41:12.000Z","msg":"g持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a9afc